{"tid":1468353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"捉鬼方針","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:06:50.000Z","uid":151439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"28ceb45fdc5f80512b654f0546c0c8df1580796c","tid":1468353,"uid":151439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:24:48.000Z","msg":"所有人而家都隨時都會身處係人群既中心，隨時隻鬼就係你旁邊被捉到然後迅間超多人圍住。後面會人叫你停手叫你冷靜，都會有人食花生，呢啲人無傷害的大家唔洗理佢，自己判斷去做認為想做同應該做既事。另一班就係係後面煽動人群去做某啲行為，而呢班就係我地最需要小心既人。<br />\n<br />\n最簡單，邊個屢次出聲叫人做某啲行為，呢個時候就大家退後啲，讓個場俾佢做佢想做既野。<br />\n<br />\n佢要做咪自己做囉，做咩要叫人地做？唔做既大家可以直接忽略呢條友，叫佢死開，唔好係到牙文班武。<br />\n<br />\n我地要捉既鬼係存心破壞運動既鬼，有意生事制造混亂場面，事後全身已退無穿無爛累到前線其他俾人拉既鬼。<br />\n<br />\n放核彈都唔割，但要同叫人放核陣自己就走左去既鬼割。"},{"pid":"c773c7f241380b4dce8711239174a43c3e60a356","tid":1468353,"uid":151439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825dece90c691962cba4013d72fb7e1877167941","tid":1468353,"uid":151439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:29:26.000Z","msg":"721721721"},{"pid":"c52f4a3d253167a0e4f0dd7791587e35d798ebbf","tid":1468353,"uid":151439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:31:54.000Z","msg":"721 721 721"},{"pid":"fa0291396bf4f32e80a8c6b1c683b4b581f9db80","tid":1468353,"uid":151439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:34:03.000Z","msg":"127 721"},{"pid":"0652592fa1c15e5f08e62a6900fec7a5d30db0f8","tid":1468353,"uid":254869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:34:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6a313b8cc187d2cb8e889b8afc88c4b026a96bd9","tid":1468353,"uid":151439,"like":0,"disli